<subSubSection pageId="152" pageNumber="550" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="152.[166,1374,1245,1948]" pageId="152" pageNumber="550">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[168,522,1796,1829]" pageId="152" pageNumber="550">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Vulnerable on The IUCN Red List. The Bururi Mouse Shrew has only recently been described, based on a single specimen. The species is probably threatened by the degradation and loss of habitat.
</paragraph>
